title: One Piece Episode 373 Review
author: deculture
description: Blog review of Episode 373 from when it originally aired. The reviewer notes that while the episode wasn't as epic as it could have been, Moria's Shadow Asgard transformation was beautifully animated. Also discusses the debut of the We Are remix opening.
